    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a great deal on a car that's ready to work for you! This vehicle is in fair condition and shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid and dependable choice for anyone looking for value. It's a functional ride that gets the job done and offers a fantastic entry point for a budget-conscious buyer!",
