    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, providing a dependable driving experience for its next owner. While it shows some minor signs of standard use consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. You can expect a solid, well-performing car that is ready for daily use without any immediate mechanical concerns.",
