    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the most discerning collector or enthusiast a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality. This is an investment-grade offering for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
